node.text: My hardest days are my best days because that’s when I battle my biggest competitor which is my mind. We get to choose what we want to be so please make sure that you are aware of what you are becoming. ☺️💪🏻✌🏻

node.text: On my 24th year on planet Earth now. I was on vacation with my family in Miami and my sweet boyfriend surprised me at 11:54 p.m to spend the whole bday with me! 😩💕🙏🏻 Now we are here exploring all of Miami! 🗣

node.text: Healthy but I used to be so lean and I absolutely disliked how I looked still lol. So trust me when I say that reaching your fitness goals will not satisfy you if you aren’t already happy with the way you look. Eat healthy, workout and remember to love yourself NOW! I am insecure literally 98% of the time and I’m switching my mindset to accept my body rather than be so consumed by the thoughts that run through my mind. ☺️🙏🏻
